Package com.alexkasko.rest.handlers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExceptionHandler
    Used on exception happened during request processing
    NotFoundHandler
    Used when no handler can be found for provided request
    RestHandler
    Empty interface to stress distinction between transport and application request processing.
    TransportHandler<T extends RestHandler>
    Transport level request handling.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultExceptionHandler
    Default ExceptionHandler implementation, returns plain-text 500 with stacktrace
    DefaultNotFoundHandler
    Default implementation of NotFoundHandler, returns plain-text 404 with registered handlers list.
    HandlersDispatcher
    Dispatches request using handlers registry matching with regular expression.
    HandlersDispatcher.Builder
    Builder class for HandlersDispatcher
    HandlersDispatcherServlet
    Dispatcher servlet for handlers, delegates GET, POST and PUT dispatching to HandlersDispatcher.
    HandlersMappingEntry<T extends RestHandler>
    Handler URL mapping entry, used in HandlersDispatcher.builder().
    HandlersSubmapping
    List of handlers mappings for submodules configuration
